OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly cloud will break to sunny
OL,6,Fspells, and with light and variable
OL,7,Fwinds it will be feeling warm. Cloud
OL,8,Fwill thicken again at times through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon, and the odd spot of
OL,10,Frain cannot be ruled out in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud breaking at times
OL,13,Fovernight, with clear spells allowing
OL,14,Fthe odd patch of mist and fog to
OL,15,Fdevelop. Perhaps staying cloudier
OL,16,Facross the Pennines, but likely
OL,17,Fstaying dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
FL,165,160,301,260,100,100
