PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F164A1775624629
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FThickening cloud through the
OL,6,Fmorning, with a band of mostly light
OL,7,Frain spreading east. This clearing by
OL,8,Fmid-afternoon to colder and breezier
OL,9,Fbut also brighter conditions, with
OL,10,Foccasional blustery showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCold
OL,13,Fstart Friday, with some frost, then
OL,14,Fsunny intervals. Rain and stronger
OL,15,Fwinds overnight, with further
OL,16,Foutbreaks of rain Saturday. Sunshine
OL,17,Fand showers Sunday. Temperatures near
OL,18,Fnormal for April.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
